OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,FWords by ITV News producer Lilly
OL,7,FCroucher
OL,9,FChocolate prices are expected to rise
OL,10,Fthis year as the cocoa market hits a
OL,11,Frecord high - but what does this mean
OL,12,Ffor our favourite Easter treats?
OL,14,FFood inflation is still higher than
OL,15,Fseveral years ago but remained mostly
OL,16,Funchanged over the last year, but
OL,17,Fchocolate prices have continued to
OL,18,Frise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
