OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,FThe price of chocolate increased by
OL,7,Falmost 12% in December compared to the
OL,8,Fprevious year, with large bars in
OL,9,Fparticular being affected.
OL,11,FWhy is the price of our favourite
OL,12,Fsweet treats so high?
OL,14,FAccording to market data from the
OL,15,FFinancial Times, cocoa market prices
OL,16,Fwere up 143% on January 15 compared to
OL,17,Fthe same time a year previously.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
