OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,FShe explained that supply chains are
OL,7,Fdifficult to create, especially with
OL,8,Fdeveloping countries, and it all
OL,9,Fstarts with the farmers who "need to
OL,10,Fearn a fair living".
OL,12,F"Chocolate bars are getting thinner -
OL,13,Fincluding Easter eggs - as big
OL,14,Fcompanies continue to try to turn a
OL,15,Fprofit."
OL,17,F"And with the increase of these prices
OL,18,Fwe are now seeing the premiumisation
OL,19,Fof these products," she added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
