OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,FHow has this affected independent UK
OL,7,Fchocolatiers?
OL,9,FFor smaller businesses, the cocoa
OL,10,Fmarket has increased the price of
OL,11,Fingredients and squeezed profit
OL,12,Fmargins.
OL,14,FElla McKay, founder of independent
OL,15,Fchocolate maker, FATSO, said her
OL,16,Fcompany's costs have doubled within
OL,17,Fthe past 18 months, but added the
OL,18,Findustry hadn't seen any "meaningful
OL,19,Fprices increases" for around 15 years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
