OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,F"For us buying direct from farmers, we
OL,7,Fcan be assured much of the increased
OL,8,Fcosts is going back to them," she said.
OL,10,F"That's definitely not the case across
OL,11,Fthe industry, with corporates making
OL,12,Fmore than ever and farmers being
OL,13,Fsqueezed even more."
OL,15,FClaire Burnet, founder of Chococo,
OL,16,Fsays we need to "rethink" chocolate
OL,17,Fand "stop thinking of it as a cheap
OL,18,Fsweet food".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
