OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,FShe says it needs to be treated with
OL,7,Fthe same respect that craft coffee,
OL,8,Fwines or olives oils are given.
OL,10,FFor her chocolate business it has been
OL,11,F"one of our toughest (years) yet",
OL,12,Fwith global events such as Brexit and
OL,13,Fthe Ukraine war creating challenges
OL,14,Ffor supply chains, as well as the
OL,15,Fdifficulties caused by the ever-
OL,16,Fchanging cocoa market.
