OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,F"We are working very closely with our
OL,7,Fchocolate partners in Ecuador and
OL,8,FColombia especially and for the last
OL,9,Fyear have been trying to work out when
OL,10,Fare the best times to place our future
OL,11,Forders," Ms Burnet said.
OL,13,F"We thought it had settled last autumn
OL,14,Fafter the peak in April, but it then
OL,15,Frocketed up again just before
OL,16,FChristmas to a new peak and has yet to
OL,17,Fcome back down," she added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
