OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,F"We will do our very best to keep our
OL,7,Fprices competitive by keeping tight
OL,8,Fcontrol of all our other costs, but
OL,9,Fgiven we are already a small lean
OL,10,Fbusiness and are now buying chocolate
OL,11,Fat more than double historic prices,
OL,12,Fwe cannot absorb all of these cost
OL,13,Fincreases and still be a sustainable
OL,14,Fbusiness."
OL,16,FWhat are the big brands saying?
OL,18,FOne brand that has seen resounding
OL,19,Fsuccess in the chocolate market is
OL,20,Fpremium ethical brand, Tony's
OL,21,FChocolonely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
