OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,FThe chocolatier, which focuses on the
OL,7,Fwelfare of its cocoa farmers, said it
OL,8,Fhas seen prices increase around 70%
OL,9,Fbut warned "high prices on the cocoa
OL,10,Ftrading market don't necessarily mean
OL,11,Fhigher prices paid to cocoa farmers".
OL,13,FBen Greensmith, UK manager for Tony's
OL,14,FChocolonely, said shoppers are likely
OL,15,Fto be paying more for their products
OL,16,Fthis Easter compared to last year
OL,17,Fbased on what the company is seeing in
OL,18,Fstores.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
