OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,F"Over the last eight months we've seen
OL,7,Fmost big chocolate companies pass on
OL,8,Fincreases of around 30-50% so
OL,9,Fchocolate is getting more expensive in
OL,10,Fthe shops as a result," he said.
OL,12,F"We've also seen some manufacturers
OL,13,Fmove away from cocoa and replace it
OL,14,Fwith more sugar and other
OL,15,Fingredients," he added.
