OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,FMr Greensmith said the Dutch chocolate
OL,7,Fbrand would "not reduce the amount of
OL,8,Fcocoa in our bars" and instead will
OL,9,Ffocus on growing volume, and the
OL,10,Fvolume of cocoa it sources, so they
OL,11,Fcan "help more farmers by enabling
OL,12,Fthem to earn a living income".
OL,14,FThis week, Lindt reported "strong
OL,15,Forganic growth" of 7.8% in 2024 but
OL,16,Fdespite this, the Swiss chocolate
OL,17,Fbrand has admitted it had been a
OL,18,F"challenging year characterised by
OL,19,Frecord high cocoa costs, substantial
OL,20,Fprice increases, and weakened consumer
OL,21,Fsentiment".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
