OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,FMondelez International, which owns
OL,7,FCadbury and Milka, said they have also
OL,8,Fbeen feeling the economic pressures
OL,9,Facross their supply chains and have
OL,10,Fhad to make certain price increases.
OL,12,F"We understand the economic pressures
OL,13,Fthat consumers continue to face and
OL,14,Fraising prices is a last resort for
OL,15,Four business," the company said in a
OL,16,Fstatement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
