OL,3,CWhy your chocolate eggs may be more
OL,4,Cexpensive this Easter
OL,6,F"We are continuing to experience
OL,7,Fsignificantly higher input costs
OL,8,Facross our supply chain, with
OL,9,Fingredients such as cocoa and dairy
OL,10,Fwhich are widely used in our products,
OL,11,Fcosting far more than they have done
OL,12,Fpreviously.
OL,14,F"Meanwhile, other costs like energy
OL,15,Fand transport also remain high. This
OL,16,Fmeans that our products continue to be
OL,17,Fmuch more expensive to make and while
OL,18,Fwe have absorbed these costs where
OL,19,Fpossible, we still face considerable
OL,20,Fchallenges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
